19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 272 of Title 19, unless there is
21 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 All county offices and courts shall offer the option to pay via
23 credit card for all transactions except where provided in Section
24 3127 of Title 68 as it states that such real estate will be sold to
